name: Autobreeder (lite) by Harm van den Dorpel

metadata.name: Autobreeder (lite)
metadata.description:
[Jakeyboy Ricc Whauden](https://deathimitateslanguage.harmvandendorpel.com/language/6e8fa363d260ac2c57addbf96fd2423cee66c600) was born November 15th 2016   

[View Autobreeder (lite) web version](https://deathimitateslanguage.harmvandendorpel.com/autobreeder/cropped.html)   

This fullscreen software autosurfs the massive genealogy of the 'death imitates language' project, containing the first 12.000 specimen, bred by a genetic algorithm, and selected by micro-feedback of the artist   

offline, duration infinite, not interactive, silent   

By Harm van den Dorpel, 2016   

This Ethereum NFT version was programmed and deployed in 2018. A maximum of 100 tokens can be minted.   

The artist retains all copyrights of the assets referenced by this NFT.
